title: Windows 10 Spring Creators Update Final Release EN-GB 17133.1
description: This is the RS4 Windows 10 Spring Creators Update EN-GB Final Release that will be released to consumers April 10, 2018 Any changes to this final version will only be made by Windows Update. No updates install on a clean install from this ISO. It is NOT cracked! You'll need to have already installed Windows 10 or have a valid licence key to do a activate a clean install of this ISO. No need to illegally crack Windows 10 when you can buy a legit key on eBay for about $10. It has Windows 10 Pro and Home including the 'N' versions. You'll need at least an 8GB USB to make the install media. Download RUFUS here to make a GPT install USB. https://rufus.akeo.ie/ The ISO was made using the ESD files from the UUP Dump website found on the My Digital Life forums. Go there no learn how do make this ISO yourself
